      <title>世界银行敦促巴基斯坦加倍投资以促进增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/world-bank-urges-pakistan-to-double-investment-to-boost-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行一位高级官员表示，巴基斯坦必须简化法规并使其经济前景可预测，以吸引更多投资并大幅刺激经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/world-bank-urges-pakistan-to-double-investment-to-boost-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 07:13:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯被告知要诚实面对放松管制的政治风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/reeves-told-to-be-honest-about-political-risks-of-deregulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府促进增长的新想法其实是老招数：有利于企业的放松管制。对于资金紧张、已经加税的工党政府来说，这种做法的吸引力在于它是免费的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/reeves-told-to-be-honest-about-political-risks-of-deregulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
